/* REXX  SPLIT PDS OF ANY ATTRIBUTES                *
 * THEPDS = "'USERID.ABC.XYZ'"                      *
 * Relies on "LISTDS "THEPDS" MEMBERS" to produce   *
 * 1 USERID.ABC.XYZ                                 *
 * 2 --RECFM-LRECL-BLKSIZE-DSORG                    *
 * 3   VB    255   27998   PO                       *
 * 4 --VOLUMES--                                    *
 * 5   VOLSER                                       *
 * 6 --MEMBERS--                                    *
 * 7   AMEMBER1                                     */
/* REXX - GENERATE ./ ADD NAME= OUTPUT */
/* Version 0.1 */
